OL,3,CFamily farm 'saddened' after produce
OL,4,Callegedly stolen from honesty box
OL,6,FA farming family say they are "really
OL,7,Fsaddened" after their produce was
OL,8,Fallegedly stolen from a new honesty
OL,9,Fbox.
OL,11,FCarre Farms had only set up the stall
OL,12,Fnext to a bus stop on La Grande Route
OL,13,FDe Saint Lawrence at the weekend.
OL,15,FLike many across the island, it is
OL,16,Funmanned and open 24/7, relying on
OL,17,Fcustomers' goodwill to pay for
OL,18,Fproducts by putting money in an
OL,19,Fhonesty box.
