OL,3,CFamily farm 'saddened' after produce
OL,4,Callegedly stolen from honesty box
OL,6,FPosting on Facebook, Carre Farms said:
OL,7,F"We added a new honesty hut to make
OL,8,Four potatoes more accessible for all
OL,9,Fislanders, so it really saddens us
OL,10,Fthat we have had nine bags taken over
OL,11,Ftwo days without being paid for.
OL,13,F"Please remember to pay for what you
OL,14,Ftake. We work extremely hard and find
OL,15,Fthings like this very disheartening."
OL,17,FThe Carre's have been farming across
OL,18,Fthree generations in Jersey since 1978
OL,19,Fand many have reacted with anger to
OL,20,Fthe news on social media.
