OL,3,CFamily farm 'saddened' after produce
OL,4,Callegedly stolen from honesty box
OL,6,FAnita Mackenzie wrote: "This is not
OL,7,Fthe Jersey I grew up in! To steal from
OL,8,Fsomeone who works hard to bring us
OL,9,Ffresh produce is disgraceful. Hope
OL,10,Fthey're ashamed of themselves!"
OL,12,FSue Davey added: "Disgusting. Never
OL,13,Fhad this years ago in Jersey, you work
OL,14,Fhard enough without people stealing
OL,15,Ffrom you."
